       1075838979,    1075850685,  t.lock_on_bulk_load,
       1075838979,    1075850726,  t.text_in_row_limit,
       1075838979,    1075850684,  t.large_value_types_out_of_row,
       1075838979,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075851024,  case when ctt.object_id IS NOT NULL then 1 else 0 end,
       1075838979,    1075851053,  t.lock_escalation_desc,
       1075838979,    1075851222,  case when ctt.object_id IS NOT NULL then case ctt.is_track_columns_updated_on when 1 then 'ON' else 'OFF' end end,
       1075838979,    1075850882,  case objectproperty(t.object_id, 'TableHasVarDecimalStorageFormat') when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838979,    1075852284,  case when t.is_memory_optimized = 1 then 1 when t.is_filetable = 1 then 2 else 0 end,
       1075838979,    1075852294,  ft.directory_name,
       1075838979,    1075852295,  ft.filename_collation_name,
       1075838979,    1075852285,  case t.durability when 1 then 0 else 1 end 
FROM sys.tables t 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.indexes i on t.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id in (0, 1) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.change_tracking_tables ctt on ctt.object_id = t.object_id

WHERE t.object_id = 1125579048 AND t.is_external=0 AND t.temporal_type <> 1

--[2022-10-11 00:04:59] Attribute CheckConstraints
SELECT 1075839020,    1075849133,  case when c.rule_object_id <> 0 then c.rule_object_id else cc.object_id end,
       1075839020,    1073742126,  o.name,
       1075839020,    1075850737,  SCHEMA_NAME(o.schema_id),
       1075839020,    1075848986,  case when cc.definition <> '' then cc.definition else sm.definition end,
       1075839020,    1075852160,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cast ( 0 as bit ) else cast ( 1 as bit ) end,
       1075839169,    1073742126,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then o.name else '%ColumnCheckConstraintName' end,
       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,
       1075839169,    1075849722,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 end,
       1075839169,    1075849061,  o.object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 1125579048 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,

       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 901578250

--[2022-10-11 00:05:00] Entity PartitionColumns

       1075839259,    1075849017,  COL_NAME(t.object_id, ic.column_id)

       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1701581100

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1701581100 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075839020,    1075852160,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cast ( 0 as bit ) else cast ( 1 as bit ) end,
       1075839169,    1073742126,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then o.name else '%ColumnCheckConstraintName' end,
       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,

         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1893581784

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects o ON c.default_object_id = o.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE   c.object_id = 2101582525 AND     c.default_object_id > 0

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 2101582525

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,

       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions

       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 2099048 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 2099048 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,
       'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),    1075839244,  1075851399,
       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,
       data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 2099048 END ELSE BEGIN IF exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 2099048) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression

       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 98099390 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,
       1075839169,    1075849722,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 end,
       1075839169,    1075849061,  o.object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 702625546 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)
--Parameter 1 = 702625546
--[2022-10-11 00:05:02] Return from Query - 0 rows

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,

       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 702625546

--[2022-10-11 00:05:02] Entity Triggers

       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.uses_native_compilation = 1 then 'TM' else tr.type end,

       1075839021,    1075850711,  sm.is_schema_bound

       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075839169,    1075849722,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 end,
       1075839169,    1075849061,  o.object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 1077578877 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1077578877

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1333579789

FROM sys.tables t

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,

       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1381579960

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1429580131

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1493580359

       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075839169,    1073742126,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then o.name else '%ColumnCheckConstraintName' end,
       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,

         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id

       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 274100017

--[2022-10-11 00:05:05] Entity DataCompression
IF exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 274100017 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN if exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 274100017 and partition_number > 1 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 274100017 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,
       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 274100017 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 274100017 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,
       'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),    1075839244,  1075851399,
       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,
       data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 274100017 END ELSE BEGIN IF exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 274100017) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 274100017 END END END

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 418100530 
ORDER BY i.index_id
--Parameter 1 = 418100530

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 450100644

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,

       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

--[2022-10-11 00:05:06] Entity DataCompression

       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075849004,  case i.is_unique when 1 then 'AK' else 'IE' end,

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1157579162 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1733581214 
ORDER BY i.index_id
--Parameter 1 = 1733581214

ORDER BY ic.partition_ordinal

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 482100758
--Parameter 1 = 482100758

       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,

--[2022-10-11 00:05:08] Entity PartitionColumns
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,
       1075839261,    1075851246,  ic.partition_ordinal,
       1075839259,    1075849017,  COL_NAME(t.object_id, ic.column_id) 
FROM sys.tables t 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.indexes i on t.object_id = i.object_id and (i.index_id = 0 or i.type = 1) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partition_schemes ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.index_columns ic on t.object_id = ic.object_id and (ic.index_id = 0 or i.type = 1) and partition_ordinal > 0 
WHERE ic.partition_ordinal > 0 AND  t.object_id = 482100758 
ORDER BY ic.partition_ordinal
--Parameter 1 = 482100758
--[2022-10-11 00:05:08] Return from Query - 0 rows


--[2022-10-11 00:05:08] Entity DataCompression
IF exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 482100758 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN if exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 482100758 and partition_number > 1 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 482100758 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,
       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 482100758 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 482100758 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,
       'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),    1075839244,  1075851399,
       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,
       data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 482100758 END ELSE BEGIN IF exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 482100758) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 482100758 END END END

       1075839170,    1075849083,  c.default_object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM    sys.columns c

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 770101784

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075839259,    1075849017,  COL_NAME(t.object_id, ic.column_id) 
FROM sys.tables t

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 914102297 
ORDER BY i.index_id

FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 1010102639 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1074102867

--[2022-10-11 00:05:10] Entity DataCompression
IF exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 1074102867 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN if exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 1074102867 and partition_number > 1 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1074102867 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1122103038 
ORDER BY i.index_id

FROM sys.indexes i

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1186103266

--[2022-10-11 00:05:11] Entity TemporalProperties
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075852336,  case t.temporal_type when 0 then cast( 0 as bit ) else cast( 1 as bit ) end,

       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1266103551 
ORDER BY i.index_id

FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 1330103779 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1330103779

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1230627427

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1230627427 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1390627997 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075839020,    1075852160,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cast ( 0 as bit ) else cast ( 1 as bit ) end,
       1075839169,    1073742126,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then o.name else '%ColumnCheckConstraintName' end,
       1075839169,    1075850574,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_disabled end,
       1075839169,    1075850818,  case when cc.is_not_trusted = 0 then cast (1 as bit) else cast (0 as bit) end,
       1075839169,    1075849722,  case when c.rule_object_id = 0 then cc.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 end,
       1075839169,    1075849061,  o.object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM sys.columns c left outer join sys.check_constraints cc ON c.object_id = cc.parent_object_id AND c.column_id = cc.parent_column_id left outer join sys.objects o ON c.rule_object_id = o.object_id OR cc.object_id = o.object_id left outer join sys.sql_modules sm ON sm.object_id = o.object_id 
WHERE c.object_id = 1502628396 and (c.rule_object_id > 0 or cc.parent_column_id = c.column_id)

       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1502628396

       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression

       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1502628396 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 1502628396 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,
       'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),    1075839244,  1075851399,
       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,
       data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1502628396 END ELSE BEGIN IF exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 1502628396) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression

       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,

       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1582628681

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1582628681 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075839019,    1075849133,  o.object_id,

       1075839170,    1073742126,  case when o.parent_Object_id <> 0 then o.name else '%ColumnDefaultConstraintName' end,
       1075839170,    1075849083,  c.default_object_id ,
         c.column_id 
FROM    sys.columns c
