       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1378103950

--[2022-10-11 00:05:14] Entity PartitionColumns

       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,
       1075839261,    1075851246,  ic.partition_ordinal,

--[2022-10-11 00:05:14] Entity DataCompression

       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1378103950 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,
       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1378103950 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 1378103950 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,
       'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),    1075839244,  1075851399,
       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,
       data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1378103950 END ELSE BEGIN IF exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 1378103950) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1378103950 END END END

--[2022-10-11 00:05:14] Entity Triggers
SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.uses_native_compilation = 1 then 'TM' else tr.type end,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger,
       1075839021,    1075850711,  sm.is_schema_bound 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id

       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1602104748

       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id

       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

FROM sys.partitions

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id

       1075838979,    1075850882,  case objectproperty(t.object_id, 'TableHasVarDecimalStorageFormat') when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,

FROM sys.tables t

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.change_tracking_tables ctt on ctt.object_id = t.object_id

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

--[2022-10-11 00:05:17] Entity PartitionColumns
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,
       1075839261,    1075851246,  ic.partition_ordinal,
       1075839259,    1075849017,  COL_NAME(t.object_id, ic.column_id) 
FROM sys.tables t

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partition_schemes ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id

SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1922105888
--Parameter 1 = 1922105888

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849459,  case i.is_unique_constraint when 1 then cast(1 as bit) else cast(0 as bit) end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 1922105888

--[2022-10-11 00:05:17] Entity PartitionColumns
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,
       1075839261,    1075851246,  ic.partition_ordinal,
       1075839259,    1075849017,  COL_NAME(t.object_id, ic.column_id) 
FROM sys.tables t 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.indexes i on t.object_id = i.object_id and (i.index_id = 0 or i.type = 1) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partition_schemes ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.index_columns ic on t.object_id = ic.object_id and (ic.index_id = 0 or i.type = 1) and partition_ordinal > 0 
WHERE ic.partition_ordinal > 0 AND  t.object_id = 1922105888 
ORDER BY ic.partition_ordinal
--Parameter 1 = 1922105888
--[2022-10-11 00:05:17] Return from Query - 0 rows


--[2022-10-11 00:05:17] Entity DataCompression
IF exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 1922105888 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN if exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 1922105888 and partition_number > 1 and index_id IN (0,1)) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1922105888 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,
       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1922105888 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 1922105888 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,
       'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),    1075839244,  1075851399,
       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,
       data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1922105888 END ELSE BEGIN IF exists (select * from  sys.partitions where object_id = 1922105888) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,    1073742126,  'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ),
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1922105888 END END END

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 30623152 
ORDER BY i.index_id

       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

FROM sys.partitions

FROM sys.partitions

--[2022-10-11 00:05:19] Entity PartitionColumns

       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,

       1075839259,    1075849017,  COL_NAME(t.object_id, ic.column_id)

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,

       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id

       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 1 AND i.type <> 5 AND i.type <> 6 AND i.object_id = 430624577

       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,
       1075839261,    1075851246,  ic.partition_ordinal,
       1075839259,    1075849017,  COL_NAME(t.object_id, ic.column_id)

WHERE ic.partition_ordinal > 0 AND  t.object_id = 430624577 
ORDER BY ic.partition_ordinal

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,

FROM sys.indexes i

LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id

       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,

       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075850212,  k.name,
       1075838985,    1075851043,  case dfs.type when 'FD' then case when t.filestream_data_space_id > 0 then t.filestream_data_space_id end else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849420,  case s.no_recompute when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852286,  case i.type when 7 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.stats s on s.object_id = i.object_id and i.index_id = s.stats_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.hash_indexes hi on i.object_id = hi.object_id and i.index_id = hi.index_id

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,

FROM sys.indexes i

       1075838979,    1075850698,  ds.data_space_id,

       1075838985,    1075851044,  case dfs.type when 'PS' then t.filestream_data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075849143,  case i.has_filter when 1 then i.filter_definition else NULL end,

       1075838985,    1075852292,  case i.type when 7 then hi.bucket_count else 1 end,

--[2022-10-11 00:05:21] Entity DataCompression

       1075839244,    1075851399,  partition_number,
       1075839244,    1075848978,  data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1182627256 AND index_id IN (0,1) END ELSE BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,
       1073742126,    'Data_Compression_'+ltrim( str( partition_number ) ) ,  1075839244,
       1075848978,    data_compression 
FROM sys.partitions 
WHERE object_id = 1182627256 AND index_id IN (0,1) END END ELSE BEGIN if exists (select * from sys.partitions where object_id = 1182627256 and partition_number > 1) BEGIN SELECT  DISTINCT 1075839244,  1073742126,

       partition_number,    1075839244,  1075848978,

FROM sys.partitions

--[2022-10-11 00:05:21] Entity ColumnStoreIndex
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075839338,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075839338,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075839338,    1075850519,  case i.type when 5 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839338,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075839338,    1075849143,  i.filter_definition,
       1075839338,    1075852470,  i.compression_delay,
       1075839338,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.partitions p on i.object_id = p.object_id and i.index_id = p.index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables t on t.object_id = i.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces dfs on dfs.data_space_id = t.filestream_data_space_id 
WHERE (i.type = 5 OR i.type = 6) AND i.object_id = 1182627256
--Parameter 1 = 1182627256

       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),

       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.uses_native_compilation = 1 then 'TM' else tr.type end,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger,
       1075839021,    1075850711,  sm.is_schema_bound 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 1182627256

--[2022-10-11 00:05:21] Entity TemporalProperties
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838979,    1075852336,  case t.temporal_type when 0 then cast( 0 as bit ) else cast( 1 as bit ) end,
       1075838979,    1075852337,  '[' + s.name + '].[' + ht.name + ']',
       1075838979,    1075852338,  case c.generated_always_type when 1 then c.name else NULL end,
       1075838979,    1075852339,  case c.generated_always_type when 2 then c.name else NULL end 
FROM sys.tables t 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.tables ht on ht.object_id = t.history_table_id AND ht.temporal_type = 1 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.schemas s on ht.schema_id = s.schema_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.columns c on c.object_id=t.object_id 
WHERE t.object_id = 1182627256 AND t.temporal_type <> 0 AND c.generated_always_type <> 0
--Parameter 1 = 1182627256

--[2022-10-11 00:05:22] View ViewPropertiesSelect
--[2022-10-11 00:05:22] View OwnerFilter
SELECT v.has_opaque_metadata,    s.is_schema_bound,  s.definition,
         case when s.definition = null then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end 
FROM sys.all_views v left outer join sys.all_sql_modules s on v.object_id = s.object_id 
WHERE v.object_id = 423672557 AND schema_id IN (SCHEMA_ID('db_accessadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_backupoperator'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_ddladmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_owner'),SCHEMA_ID('db_securityadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('dbo'),SCHEMA_ID('guest'),SCHEMA_ID('HumanResources'),SCHEMA_ID('INFORMATION_SCHEMA'),SCHEMA_ID('Person'),SCHEMA_ID('Production'),SCHEMA_ID('Purchasing'),SCHEMA_ID('Sales'))

--[2022-10-11 00:05:22] View Triggers
SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 423672557
--Parameter 1 = 423672557
--[2022-10-11 00:05:22] Return from Query - 0 rows

SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 439672614

SELECT v.has_opaque_metadata,    s.is_schema_bound,  s.definition,
         case when s.definition = null then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end 
FROM sys.all_views v left outer join sys.all_sql_modules s on v.object_id = s.object_id

--[2022-10-11 00:05:22] View Triggers
SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 455672671
--Parameter 1 = 455672671
--[2022-10-11 00:05:22] Return from Query - 0 rows

--[2022-10-11 00:05:23] View OwnerFilter
SELECT v.has_opaque_metadata,    s.is_schema_bound,  s.definition,
         case when s.definition = null then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end 
FROM sys.all_views v left outer join sys.all_sql_modules s on v.object_id = s.object_id 
WHERE v.object_id = 487672785 AND schema_id IN (SCHEMA_ID('db_accessadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_backupoperator'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_ddladmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_owner'),SCHEMA_ID('db_securityadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('dbo'),SCHEMA_ID('guest'),SCHEMA_ID('HumanResources'),SCHEMA_ID('INFORMATION_SCHEMA'),SCHEMA_ID('Person'),SCHEMA_ID('Production'),SCHEMA_ID('Purchasing'),SCHEMA_ID('Sales'))

--[2022-10-11 00:05:23] View Triggers
SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 487672785
--Parameter 1 = 487672785
--[2022-10-11 00:05:23] Return from Query - 0 rows

SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 503672842
--Parameter 1 = 503672842
--[2022-10-11 00:05:23] Return from Query - 0 rows

--[2022-10-11 00:05:23] View OwnerFilter
SELECT v.has_opaque_metadata,    s.is_schema_bound,  s.definition,
         case when s.definition = null then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end 
FROM sys.all_views v left outer join sys.all_sql_modules s on v.object_id = s.object_id 
WHERE v.object_id = 519672899 AND schema_id IN (SCHEMA_ID('db_accessadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_backupoperator'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_ddladmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_owner'),SCHEMA_ID('db_securityadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('dbo'),SCHEMA_ID('guest'),SCHEMA_ID('HumanResources'),SCHEMA_ID('INFORMATION_SCHEMA'),SCHEMA_ID('Person'),SCHEMA_ID('Production'),SCHEMA_ID('Purchasing'),SCHEMA_ID('Sales'))

SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 519672899

--[2022-10-11 00:05:23] View Triggers
SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 535672956
--Parameter 1 = 535672956
--[2022-10-11 00:05:23] Return from Query - 0 rows

SELECT v.has_opaque_metadata,    s.is_schema_bound,  s.definition,
         case when s.definition = null then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end 
FROM sys.all_views v left outer join sys.all_sql_modules s on v.object_id = s.object_id 
WHERE v.object_id = 551673013 AND schema_id IN (SCHEMA_ID('db_accessadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_backupoperator'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_ddladmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_owner'),SCHEMA_ID('db_securityadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('dbo'),SCHEMA_ID('guest'),SCHEMA_ID('HumanResources'),SCHEMA_ID('INFORMATION_SCHEMA'),SCHEMA_ID('Person'),SCHEMA_ID('Production'),SCHEMA_ID('Purchasing'),SCHEMA_ID('Sales'))

--[2022-10-11 00:05:24] View KeyConstraints
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075849004,  case i.is_unique when 1 then 'AK' else 'IE' end,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.object_id = 567673070 
ORDER BY i.index_id
--Parameter 1 = 567673070
--[2022-10-11 00:05:24] Return from Query - 0 rows


--[2022-10-11 00:05:24] View Triggers
SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 567673070
--Parameter 1 = 567673070
--[2022-10-11 00:05:24] Return from Query - 0 rows

--[2022-10-11 00:05:24] View OwnerFilter
SELECT v.has_opaque_metadata,    s.is_schema_bound,  s.definition,
         case when s.definition = null then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end 
FROM sys.all_views v left outer join sys.all_sql_modules s on v.object_id = s.object_id 
WHERE v.object_id = 583673127 AND schema_id IN (SCHEMA_ID('db_accessadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_backupoperator'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_ddladmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_owner'),SCHEMA_ID('db_securityadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('dbo'),SCHEMA_ID('guest'),SCHEMA_ID('HumanResources'),SCHEMA_ID('INFORMATION_SCHEMA'),SCHEMA_ID('Person'),SCHEMA_ID('Production'),SCHEMA_ID('Purchasing'),SCHEMA_ID('Sales'))
--Parameter 1 = 583673127

       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id

SELECT v.has_opaque_metadata,    s.is_schema_bound,  s.definition,
         case when s.definition = null then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end 
FROM sys.all_views v left outer join sys.all_sql_modules s on v.object_id = s.object_id 
WHERE v.object_id = 599673184 AND schema_id IN (SCHEMA_ID('db_accessadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_backupoperator'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_datawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_ddladmin'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatareader'),SCHEMA_ID('db_denydatawriter'),SCHEMA_ID('db_owner'),SCHEMA_ID('db_securityadmin'),SCHEMA_ID('dbo'),SCHEMA_ID('guest'),SCHEMA_ID('HumanResources'),SCHEMA_ID('INFORMATION_SCHEMA'),SCHEMA_ID('Person'),SCHEMA_ID('Production'),SCHEMA_ID('Purchasing'),SCHEMA_ID('Sales'))

SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 599673184
--Parameter 1 = 599673184

SELECT 1075839021,    1073742126,  tr.name,
       1075839021,    1075849133,  tr.object_id,
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,
       1075839021,    1075850563,  am.assembly_class,
       1075839021,    1075850670,  case when am.object_id is not NULL then NULL when sm.definition is NULL then cast ( 1 as bit ) else cast ( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,
       1075839021,    1075850838,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then sm.execute_as_principal_id when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id <> '-2' then am.execute_as_principal_id else NULL end,
       1075839021,    1075848990,  tr.is_disabled,
       1075839021,    1075850664,  tr.type ,
       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,
       1075839021,    1075848991,  tr.is_instead_of_trigger 
FROM sys.triggers tr 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.assembly_modules am on tr.object_id = am.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.objects so on tr.object_id = so.object_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_modules sm on tr.object_id = sm.object_id 
WHERE tr.parent_id = 615673241
--Parameter 1 = 615673241

--[2022-10-11 00:05:25] View KeyConstraints
SELECT DISTINCT 
       1075838985,    1073742126,  i.name,
       1075838985,    1075849133,  i.index_id,
       1075838985,    1075849004,  case i.is_unique when 1 then 'AK' else 'IE' end,
       1075838985,    1075850519,  case i.type when 1 then cast( 1 as bit ) else cast( 0 as bit ) end,
       1075838985,    1075849413,  case when i.fill_factor = 0 then NULL else i.fill_factor end,
       1075838985,    1075849418,  i.is_padded,
       1075838985,    1075850538,  i.allow_row_locks,
       1075838985,    1075850537,  i.allow_page_locks,
       1075838985,    1075849414,  i.ignore_dup_key,
       1075838985,    1075850574,  i.is_disabled,
       1075838985,    1075850675,  case ds.type when 'FG' then i.data_space_id else NULL end,
       1075838985,    1075853379,  CASE WHEN i.optimize_for_sequential_key = 1 THEN 'ON' ELSE 'OFF' END 
FROM sys.indexes i 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.key_constraints k on i.object_id = k.parent_object_id and i.index_id = k.unique_index_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.data_spaces ds on ds.data_space_id = i.data_space_id 
WHERE i.is_primary_key = 0 AND i.name is not null AND i.type <> 3 AND i.object_id = 647673355 
ORDER BY i.index_id
--Parameter 1 = 647673355
--[2022-10-11 00:05:25] Return from Query - 0 rows

       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 1),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 2),
       1075839021,    1075848978,  (select type from sys.events where object_id = tr.object_id and type = 3),
       1075839021,    1075849722,  case when tr.is_not_for_replication IS NOT NULL THEN tr.is_not_for_replication ELSE 2 END,
       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,
       1075839021,    1075850692,  am.assembly_method,

       1075839021,    1075850656,  am.assembly_id,

       1075839021,    1075850674,  case when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id is NULL then 'CALLER' when tr.type = 'TR' and sm.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' when tr.type = 'TA' and am.execute_as_principal_id = '-2'  then 'OWNER' else 'USER' end,

       1075839021,    1075848996,  sm.definition,

FROM sys.triggers tr

--[2022-10-11 00:05:26] SQLServer_Login Properties
SELECT  1075839208,    1075850668,  sp.default_database_name,
       1075839208,    1075850606,  sp.default_language_name,
       1075839208,    1075850662,  c.certificate_id,
       1075839208,    1075850547,  ak.asymmetric_key_id,
       1075839208,    1075850549,  sp.type,
       1075839208,    1075850743,  sl.sid,
       1075839208,    1075850561,  case when sl.is_expiration_checked IS NOT NULL THEN sl.is_expiration_checked else 2 end ,
       1075839208,    1075850562,  case when sl.is_policy_checked IS NOT NULL THEN sl.is_policy_checked else 2 end,
       1075839208,    1075850567,  sp.credential_id,
       1075839208,    1075850574,  sl.is_disabled 
FROM sys.server_principals sp 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.sql_logins sl on sp.principal_id = sl.principal_id 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.asymmetric_keys ak on sp.sid = ak.sid 
LEFT OUTER JOIN sys.certificates c on sp.sid = c.sid 
WHERE sp.principal_id = 101
--Parameter 1 = 101
--[2022-10-11 00:05:26] Return from Query - 1 rows
